              <span id="reviewTextContainer737521939" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14700584312225321094">A childish and frankly stupid lack of any understanding of humanity or reading of history. Not a book on anarchy at all but a lazily concealed promotion of socialism and class warfare through atheistic, Darwinian, and Marxist principles. Miserably fails in attempting to replace one utopian vision for another.</span>

          </span>
