<div id="review_2710355115" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2710355115" />
    <a title="R. Reddebrek" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/83321281-r-reddebrek"><img alt="R. Reddebrek" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1560271253p2/83321281.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2710355115?book_show_action=true">Feb 10, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="R. Reddebrek" class="user" itemprop="url" name="R. Reddebrek" href="/user/show/83321281-r-reddebrek">R. Reddebrek</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2710355115" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer988477816823714422">Another of Malatesta&apos;s short introductions to Anarchism. This one surprisingly in the process of explaining the Anarchist mindset also elaborated arguments against state socialism, and anti state capitalism, so in a way its gotten more relevant and accessible as time went on.</span>
  <span id="freeText988477816823714422" style="display:none">Another of Malatesta's short introductions to Anarchism. This one surprisingly in the process of explaining the Anarchist mindset also elaborated arguments against state socialism, and anti state capitalism, so in a way its gotten more relevant and accessible as time went on.</span>
  <a data-text-id="988477816823714422" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


