  <span id="freeText11311094481311971201" style="display:none">Oh, I suppose this is my way of celebrating May Day. Malatesta's not a bad guy. I still like reading his stuff, &amp; he knows how to create a great metaphor. I'd like to read him in Italian some time because the translations include amazing vocabulary.</span>
